high_descs: Turn to the right, go to the wall, hang a left, go to the microwave.
Pick up the yellow handled knife from the counter to the right of the microwave.
Turn to the right to the sink.
Cut the potato in the center of the sink into slices.
Put the knife in the sink.
Pick up a slice of the potato from the sink.
Turn to the left to the microwave.
Put the potato in the microwave and turn it on, remove cooked potato from the microwave.
Turn to the right to the sink.
Put potato slice in the sink to the right of the sliced potato.
anns.task_desc: Put cooked potato slice in the sink.

high_descs: Walk forward across the room to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn right to face the sink.
Cut the potato in the sink into slices.
Put the knife in the sink with the potato.
Pick up a slice of potato from in the sink.
Turn to the left to face the microwave.
Warm the potato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn right to face the sink.
Place the potato slice in the sink.
anns.task_desc: To heat a slice of potato and place it in the sink.

high_descs: move slightly to the right and then forward to the microwave
pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle that is on the counter to the right of the microwave
turn to the right to face the sink
slice the potato that is in the middle of the sink with the sharp knife
put the knife in to the sink
pick up one slice of the potato from the sink
turn to the left to face the microwave
open the microwave door, put the potato on to the plate that is in the microwave, turn on the microwave for four seconds, open the door, remove the potato slice, close the door
turn to the right to face the sink
put the potato slice in to the sink to the right of the knife
anns.task_desc: put a cooked potato slice in to the sink
